# macOS
.DS_Store

# Editor / IDE
*.swp
*~
.vscode/
.idea/

# Backups created by install.sh / uninstall.sh / the helpers
*.bak
*.bak.*

# Local shell/env overrides
.env
.env.*

# Test scratch (ruflo-parity-test writes to /tmp, but guard against stray copies)
test-*.log
.swarm/
.claude-flow/

# ruflo/agentic-qe dogfooding artifacts (created by running `ruflo init` / `aqe init` /
# `ruflo-onboard` against this repo itself — runtime output, not source).
.agentic-qe/
.claude/
*.db
# CLAUDE.md backups: `aqe init` writes CLAUDE.md.backup; `ruflo init --force` writes
# CLAUDE.md.pre-ruflo (executor.js #2208). Both are regenerable — never commit them.
CLAUDE.md.backup
CLAUDE.md.pre-ruflo
CLAUDE.md.pre-ruflo.*
# NOTE: project-local CLAUDE.md is intentionally NOT ignored here — see the open decision
# in docs/upstream/ruflo-self-improvement-findings.md / PR discussion (commit a curated
# AQE-instructions CLAUDE.md vs. fold AQE guidance into the global template).
